							.col-md-6.d-xl-none.offset-lg-1
								.side-news
									.report-num Report #1
									.report-name Security Token Offerings
									a.btn.btn-outline-white(href='/pdf/TSA_Report.pdf') Read
							.col-md-6.col-xl-6.col-lg-4.d-md-block.d-none
								.news-item
									.news-item__title
										a(href='https://medium.com/@bettertokens/betternews-5-september-to-remember-e21122749c61')
											| September
											| to remember
									.news-item__text
										| This issue covers regulatory news for September from
										| regulators in jurisdictions that are no&mldr;
									.news-item__date Oct 5
							.col-md-6.col-xl-6.col-lg-4.d-md-block.d-none
								.news-item
									.news-item__title
										a(href='https://medium.com/@bettertokens/betternews-4-luxembourg-stable-coin-regulatory-view-87f38c18238c')
											| Luxembourg:
											| Stable Coin Regulatory View
									.news-item__text
										| During last week BetterTokens co-founder and Board
										| member Artem Tolkachev and BetterTokens secretary Georgiy Gukasyan had&mldr;
									.news-item__date Sep 28
							.col-md-6.col-xl-6.col-lg-4.d-lg-block.d-none
								.news-item
									.news-item__title
										a(href='https://medium.com/@bettertokens/betternews-3-malta-dlt-system-audit-requirements-and-dlt-exchanges-9d647d7b390a')
											| Malta:
											| DLT System Audit requirements and DLT Exchanges
									.news-item__text
										| The discussion with Malta Digital Innovation Authority
